Breakdown by Categories 

 

 

At the snapshot date of 5 April 2017 GreenZone Cleaning & Support Services employed a total 308    

(42.2 %) males and 420 (57.7%) females across the organisation in a variety of roles. 

 

1.  Gender Pay Gap 

 
