It should be noted that only Head Office employees, following successful completion of the 
probationary period, qualify to earn a bonus.  On 5th April 2017, all qualifying employees received 
their bonus payment (20 males and 21 females) 

Based on this, we can say that 100% of Head office employees, both male and female, received a 
bonus. 

 

