We can see a higher percentage of women across the quartiles which appears to be in line with the 
overall employee female/male demographics.  

The Lower, Lower middle and Upper middle quartiles include cleaning operatives earning NMW and 
therefore these three categories  could be treated as one.  The Upper Quartile includes operatives 
earning above NMW,  operatives  earning  LLW  and  Head  Office  employees.  It is  worth  noting  that 
higher wages in certain contracts, including LLW are dictated by the client and not by the Company.   

 

 

 

 

 

 

Doc 030a – Issue 1 

 

